                       geant4-01-00-ref-08
                       ===================

geant4-01-00-ref-08 is a new reference tag.  The main feature is new
electromagnetic code (expect your output to change in detail).  The
problems reported with geant4-01-00-ref-07 still remain.

geant4-01-00-ref-08 is geant4-01-00-ref-07 plus:

em-V01-00-01              - New em code (details to come).
materials-V01-00-00       - const char* everywhere in
                            G4MaterialPropertiesTable.
geom-solids-csg-V01-00-05 - Trivial fixes (e.g., added explicit casts).
g3tog4-V01-00-00a         - Improvements and fixes by Bill, Ivana and Gabriele.
examples-V01-00-05        - Small fixes to extended/electromagnetic.
                          - Updated all .out files, novice and extended.
                          - Small fix for NT in TestEm4.cc.
